Lemo mikwayogo mondo olo wasik Israel


1  In Israel, hul kaka wasiki osesandi malit, chakre tinni.


2  “An Israel, wasika osesanda malit chakre tinna,

to pok giloya.


3  Ne ging’ado dieng’eya achadha marach,

mi giloke mana ka puodho mopur.


4  To Ruoth Nyasaye ma timne kare,

osechodo tonde mane joricho osetueyago.”


5  Mad lo jogo duto ma mon gi Sayun,

mi riembgi ka wigi okuot, kendo dwokgi chien!


6  Onego gichal gi lum matwi e tat ot,

to two kapok ong’adi.


7  Onge ng’ama choke kata matueye wiye wiye.


8  Kamano ji makadho ok nyal wachonigi niya,

“Waguedhou e nying Ruoth Nyasaye.”

Kata ni, “Onego Ruoth Nyasaye guedhu.”

